Package org.midao.jdbc.core.handlers.output.lazy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LazyOutputHandler<T,S>
    Lazy output handler handles output from LazyStatementHandler and allows lazy loading of data from it.
    LazyScrollOutputHandler<T,S>
    Lazy scrollable output handler handles output from LazyStatementHandler and allows lazy loading of data from it.
    LazyScrollUpdateOutputHandler<T,S>
    If underlying JDBC Driver doesn't support scrollable/updateable ResultSet - exception would be thrown.
    LazyUpdateOutputHandler<T,S>
    If underlying JDBC Driver doesn't support updateable ResultSet - exception would be thrown.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLazyOutputHandler  
    AbstractScrollUpdateLazyOutputHandler  
    BeanLazyOutputHandler<S>
    Converts query output into lazy list of beans
    BeanLazyScrollOutputHandler<S>
    Converts query output into scrollable lazy list of beans
    BeanLazyScrollUpdateOutputHandler<S>
    Converts query output into scrollable and updateable lazy list of beans
    BeanLazyUpdateOutputHandler<S>
    Converts query output into updateable lazy list of beans
    MapLazyOutputHandler
    Converts query output into List of Maps
    MapLazyScrollOutputHandler
    Converts query output into scrollable lazy list of maps
    MapLazyScrollUpdateOutputHandler
    Converts query output into scrollable and updateable lazy list of maps
    MapLazyUpdateOutputHandler
    Converts query output into updateable lazy list of maps
